Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
New Base Business Park by AVID Property Group is an 85ha master planned industrial estate located in Brendale on Brisbane's North Side. The estate is strategically located centrally within Brisbane North, being within close proximity to the Brisbane CBD and outer northern regions including Caboolture and Redcliffe.

Building Sizes: 1,000sqm - 15,000sqm. New stages 7B and 5 are the latest release in Brendale’s New Base Estate. The lots range in size from 2,364sqm through to 4,000sqm with ability to combine lots to over 2Ha.
Site Credentials

•	Lot sizes from 2,364* to 4,000sqm* and above
•	Fully serviced and level land - ready to build
•	Broad zoning allowing multitude of industry and commercial uses
•	High profile land options with future dual street accessibility
•	B-double approved routes
•	Excellent connectivity to major highways, arterial roads & public transport
•	Ideal for owner-occupiers & developers seeking a highly successful business location
•	Ability to accommodate tenants on a design and construct basis

Contact Exclusive Marketing Agents Dillon Murphy, Hugh Adnam of CBRE and Nick Bandiera, Fraser Power of JLL for more information.
